@startuml UC6: Reservation Change - Create Request Pending Exists

!theme plain

autonumber

actor User
participant "System" as System
participant "Server" as Server

== Create Change Request ==

User -> System: Press "Order Change Request" Button
System -> Server: Request Create Change Request
Server -> Server: Check Order Ownership
Server -> Server: Check Change Deadline
Server -> Server: Check Pending Requests
Server -> Server: Pending Request Found

Server -> System: Pending Request Exists Error
System -> User: Display Error Message\n("There is already a pending change request")

